data.description: Beautiful inside and out, meticulously taken care of  home on extra large lot!!! This home offers a lovely family room with vaulted ceiling tons of natural light and gorgeous fireplace!  You will love every room that has been updated with new flooring and great colors. It features  3 bedrooms on main with 2 bathrooms.  Lower level offers large walk out family room and a bonus room that can double for rec room or fourth bedroom if you add egress window! The giant backyard is ideal for out door activities and the mature trees give off great shade. New furnace, air and heat pump!!!  This home is a must see!!!
